" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 26, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sxz1764054009503.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sxz1764054009503.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sxz1764054009503.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sxz1764054009503\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The following examples are for testing purpose only. To apply these settings in\n\t\tproduction, follow the backend-specific instructions.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__section_w399ab1b5b1_w400ab1b5_w401ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246745e49\">Starting Grafana LGTM Stack</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Grafana's otel-lgtm is an all-in-one OpenTelemetry backend. To start it with docker, run the\n\t\t\t\tfollowing command:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_iq4_twy_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">docker run -p 3000:3000 -p 4317:4317 -p 4318:4318 --rm -ti grafana/otel-lgtm</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">To access OTLP HTTP Endpoint, go to <span class=\"ph filepath\">http://localhost:4318</span>. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">To access Grafana, go to <span class=\"ph filepath\">http://localhost:3000</span> and configure\n\t\t\t\tdashboards.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__section_lxv_3dz_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246745e73\">Custom Collector + Jaeger + Elasticsearch Example</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">OpenTelemetry Collector Config Example\n\t\t\t\t(otel-collector-config.yaml):<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_kvt_mdz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">receivers:\n  otlp:\n    protocols:\n      http:\n        endpoint: 0.0.0.0:4318\n\nprocessors:\n  batch: {}\n\nexporters:\n  otlp:\n    endpoint: jaeger_host:4318\n    tls:\n      insecure: true\n\n  elasticsearch/http:\n    endpoint: \"http://elasticsearch_host:9200\"\n    logs_index: \"Uniface_App-log\"\n\nservice:\n  pipelines:\n    traces:\n      receivers: [otlp]\n      exporters: [otlp]\n\n    logs:\n      receivers: [otlp]\n      processors: [batch]\n      exporters: [elasticsearch/http]\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__ul_knl_4dz_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\">Start Elasticsearch (Persistent Log\n\t\t\t\t\tStorage)<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_upv_pdz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">docker run -d --name elasticsearch   -e \"discovery.type=single-node\"   -e \"xpack.security.enabled=false\"   -p 9200:9200   docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:7.17.5</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n<li class=\"li\">Start Jaeger (Trace\n\t\t\t\t\tViewer)<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_f52_rdz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">docker run -d --name jaeger   -e COLLECTOR_OTLP_ENABLED=true   -p 16686:16686 \\  # Jaeger UI\n  -p 4317:4317 \\    # OTLP gRPC\n  -p 4318:4318 \\    # OTLP HTTP\n  jaegertracing/all-in-one:1.50</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n<li class=\"li\">Start\n\t\t\t\t\tKibana<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_4\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_rhh_rdz_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">docker run -d --name kibana   --link elasticsearch:elasticsearch   -p 5601:5601   -e \"ELASTICSEARCH_HOSTS=http://elasticsearch:9200\"   docker.elastic.co/kibana/kibana:7.17.5</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n<li class=\"li\">Start the OpenTelemetry\n\t\t\t\t\tCollector<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sxz1764054009503_html_5\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sxz1764054009503__codeblock_bkp_12z_khc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">docker run --rm -it --name otel-collector   -v $(pwd)/otel-collector-config.yaml:/etc/otel-collector-config.yaml   -p 4318:4318   otel/opentelemetry-collector-contrib:latest   --config=/etc/otel-collector-config.yaml</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24138749\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24138749\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Testing Environment Setup Examples Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 26, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The following examples are for testing purpose only. To apply these settings in production, follow the backend-specific instructions. Starting Grafana LGTM Stack Grafana's otel-lgtm is an all-in-one OpenTelemetry backend. To start it with docker, run the following command: Explain this code docker run -p 3000:3000 -p 4317:4317 -p 4318:4318 --rm -ti grafana/otel-lgtm Copy To access OTLP HTTP Endpoint, go to http://localhost:4318 . To access Grafana, go to http://localhost:3000 and configure dashboards. Custom Collector + Jaeger + Elasticsearch Example OpenTelemetry Collector Config Example (otel-collector-config.yaml): Explain this code receivers: otlp: protocols: http: endpoint: 0.0.0.0:4318 processors: batch: {} exporters: otlp: endpoint: jaeger_host:4318 tls: insecure: true elasticsearch/http: endpoint: \"http://elasticsearch_host:9200\" logs_index: \"Uniface_App-log\" service: pipelines: traces: receivers: [otlp] exporters: [otlp] logs: receivers: [otlp] processors: [batch] exporters: [elasticsearch/http] Copy Start Elasticsearch (Persistent Log Storage) Explain this code docker run -d --name elasticsearch -e \"discovery.type=single-node\" -e \"xpack.security.enabled=false\" -p 9200:9200 docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:7.17.5 Copy Start Jaeger (Trace Viewer) Explain this code docker run -d --name jaeger -e COLLECTOR_OTLP_ENABLED=true -p 16686:16686 \\ # Jaeger UI -p 4317:4317 \\ # OTLP gRPC -p 4318:4318 \\ # OTLP HTTP jaegertracing/all-in-one:1.50 Copy Start Kibana Explain this code docker run -d --name kibana --link elasticsearch:elasticsearch -p 5601:5601 -e \"ELASTICSEARCH_HOSTS=http://elasticsearch:9200\" docker.elastic.co/kibana/kibana:7.17.5 Copy Start the OpenTelemetry Collector Explain this code docker run --rm -it --name otel-collector -v $(pwd)/otel-collector-config.yaml:/etc/otel-collector-config.yaml -p 4318:4318 otel/opentelemetry-collector-contrib:latest --config=/etc/otel-collector-config.yaml Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}